author: COMSOL
description:
In this example, three parallel pipelines are protected against corrosion by an impressed current cathodic protection (ICCP) system using nine separate anodes.

The electrode potential and the total interface current density are evaluated along the pipelines to assess the performance of the corrosion protection system.
